  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dab\u0dd1\u0d9c\u0dbd\u0db1\u0dd4\u0dad\u0dca \u0d91\u0d9a\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd2\u0db1 \u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0db1\u0dca \u0d9c\u0db8\u0db1\u0dca \u0db6\u0dbd\u0db4\u0dad\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "One-day flight tickets to Kurunegala",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Ms. Piyumi Bandara, the media spokesperson of the department, said that the second step in issuing passports from the regional offices of the Immigration and Emigration Department, the issuance of passports from the Kurunegala office will start tomorrow (11) and accordingly, passports will be issued to applicants who have booked an earlier date and time.",
        "Ms. Bandara states that passports will only be issued to applicants who have reserved a date and time from the regional offices of Matara, Vavuniya, Kandy and Kurunegala under the one-day and regular services and persons who have not reserved a date and time will not be allowed to enter the head office or regional offices.",
        "She further said that a date and time can be reserved by visiting the website of the Immigration Department, Aagasapapasatoresadabagatadagakana, and the number of applicants booking dates and times has increased."
      ],
